  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I contribute money for that purpose, many others.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he spoke for about two hours to us, me and my closest friends, trying to figure out what right, what purpose, did we have to surround it, to attack so many times, to lose so many young boys.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But finally, we took it over.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We took it over to many months by sending a truck robot, without anybody, bring it to a certain spot and just, right by itself, loaded with dynamite.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we hit the wall.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I would say the wall was about six feet wide, steel and everything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we succeeded in open up an opening.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we took it over.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Was hard-- lost a lot of friends, very close friends.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But you know, life has to go on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Also, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] there was a hill right next to that fortress, which was, I would say, a quarter of a mile square, you know, round hill, which they, sit there for over a month and thinking, we're trying to attack.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we didn't succeed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Until finally, we attacked it once we had-- I would say the Israeli army had three tanks, three Sherman tanks that we stole it from the English army.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we attacked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that's how we took it over.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was 1947 until 1949.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When the war end, I still worked for the army.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And at an office.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And soldiers who used to be in my unit, they used to come to me [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to help them to get settled, which I used to help them.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] And one very memorable, not pleasant, you know, action was-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it was 1948.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
